      <guid>https://duragauge.github.io/chapter-1/1.6/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div style=&#34;position:relative; clear:both; padding:0;&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;https://duragauge.github.io/img/chapter-1/ipod-1428164_1280.jpg&#34;  title=&#34;iPod photo by mikefoster on Pixabay&#34;  alt=&#34;iPod photo by mikefoster on Pixabay&#34; style=&#34;display:block; width:100%; height:auto;&#34; &gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span style=&#34;position:absolute; height:auto; bottom:0em; right:0em; margin:0;  padding: .1em .3em;  color:white;  font-size: .8em;  background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);  text-align:right;  z-index:5;  opacity:0.65;  border-radius:.3em 0em 0em 0em;&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;a href = &#34;https://pixabay.com/photo-1428164/&#34;&gt;iPod photo by mikefoster on Pixabay&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction&#34;&gt;Introduction&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When the stock market opened on Monday, October 22, 2001, stock in Enron (a large Fortune-500 energy company) was trading for about $20 per share.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;At the same time stock in Apple (the electronics manufacturer) could also be purchased for $20.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
